posts.description: This command will grab a post from the subreddit you give it. If the subreddit has a space, just remove it. Unfortunately, you cannot save posts to your collection with this command.

unban.description: This command will unban the user provided.

reset-status.description: This command will reset your soosBot status.

tts.example: tts soosBot is a great bot!
tts.description: This command will generate a text to speech file from the text given.

meme.description:
This command will grab a meme from reddit, and will send it in the channel you are in. You can also react to the bookmark <:soosBot_save:795131937592311848> to save the meme to your collection. 
 * *See the ``saved`` command.*

previous.description: This command will play a previous song in the queue.

warn.example: warn @soos creating the best discord bot there is.
warn.description: Will DM the provided user the provided warning. As of now, there is no warn tracking.

person.description: This command will generate a person that does not exist.

event.description: This command will show the leaderboard for the previous event, or the upcoming new event's details.

purge.description: This command will delete the # of messages given from that channel. If you mention someone, it will delete their messages from the # given, `sb purge @soosBot 50` would go though the last 50 messages in the current channel and delete any that were from @soosBot. `sb purge` will defaultly delete 5 messages if no # or mention is provided.

fact.description: This command will give a random fact.

saved.description:
This command will let you browse your saved memes. 
 * *See the ``meme`` command.*

fox.description: This command will give you a random picture of a fox.

answer.example: answer is soosBot the best bot?
answer.description: This command will give an answer to the question like a 8ball

shuffle.description: This command will shuffle the queue.

bird.description: This command will give you a random picture of a bird.

roll.description: This command will roll a 6 sided die.

next.description: This command go to the next song in the queue.

queue.description: This command show the current music queue.

dog.description: This command will give you a random picture of a dog.

invite.description: This command will give a invite link for soosBot.

join.description: This command will join the current voice channel the user is in.

repeat.description:
This command will repeat the provided songs.
 Mode can be three different things:
 ``all`` will repeat all the songs in the queue
``1`` will repeat the current song
``none`` will repeat nothing.

disconnect.description: This command will leave the current voice channel the user is in.

uptime.description: This command will show how long soosBot has been online for.

weather.description: This command will give the weather of the place provided.

pause.description: This command will pause the current music track.

cat.description: This command will give you a random picture of a cat.

compile.description: This command will compile the code given the language and the code.

play.description: This command will play what if provided. If you give it a file, it will play that. If you give it a youtube link, it will play that.

urban.description: This command will check urban dictionary for the word provided.

stop.description: This command will clear the queue and stop playing the current track.

joke.description: This command will give a random joke.

love.description: This command will prompt the user to give two names, and will calculate the % of love between them. \n(Info not 100% accurate)

say.description: Sb say soosBot is the best bot.

languages.description: This command will give the user a list of programing languages the command ``compile`` supports.

ymjoke.description: This command will give a random yo momma joke.

quote.description: This command will give a random famous quote

set-status.description: This command will set your soosBot status to what is provided. Bad words will be blocked.

kick.description: This command will kick the user provided with the reason provided.

ban.description: This command will ban the user provided with the reason provided.

covid.description: This command will give covid data for the country given.

define.description: This command is not available yet.

profile.description: This command will give the profile picture and date the account was made of the user. If user is not provided, it will use the person who used the command.

flag.description: This command will give the flag, and other info about the place provided.

help.description: This command is the help command.

bingus.description: This command is a custom command. To get one, win a event or ask soos#6008

TheFatBird.description: This command is a custom command. To get one, win a event or ask soos#6008

wink.description: This command is a custom command. To get one, win a event or ask soos#6008

horny.description: This command is a custom command. To get one, win a event or ask soos#6008

whoismars.description: This command is a custom command. To get one, win a event or ask soos#6008

thanks.description: This command is a custom command. To get one, win a event or ask soos#6008

prefix.description: This command will change soosBot's prefix. Mention soosBot to view its current prefix.

translate.description: This command will translate the given text into english.

translate-to.example: translate spanish Hello, how are you?
translate-to.description: This command will translate the given text into the given language.
